23:37.316 --> 23:40.284
You want
a baby picture of me?

23:40.286 --> 23:42.720
Yeah.

23:42.722 --> 23:44.488
Yeah, you have that
effect on me.

23:44.490 --> 23:47.024
A different person...

23:47.026 --> 23:49.026
...we want different things.

23:49.028 --> 23:52.196
Real things.

23:53.598 --> 23:55.833
You...

23:55.835 --> 23:57.835
...us.

23:59.438 --> 24:02.907
Crash...

24:02.909 --> 24:08.345
