24:23.963 --> 24:25.729
I being serious, Crash.

24:25.731 --> 24:28.165
Okay, so am I.

24:29.601 --> 24:33.537
Look.

24:33.539 --> 24:34.905
You decided to go.

24:34.907 --> 24:37.908
Your life,
your decision, right?

24:37.910 --> 24:39.677
Right.

24:39.679 --> 24:40.911
Same with me.

24:40.913 --> 24:42.947
My life, my decision.

24:42.949 --> 24:46.217
