Stop it.

28:10.756 --> 28:14.658
Stop talking about me
in the past tense.

28:17.395 --> 28:18.562
Shoot me, I'm sorry.

28:18.564 --> 28:21.498
I don't know proper
fugitive etiquette.

28:23.101 --> 28:24.435
You sure you
wanna take off?

28:24.437 --> 28:25.669
