29:11.817 --> 29:13.617
"Kyle, I know you're
sleeping with my wife."

29:13.619 --> 29:15.352
Trust me, Liz,
he knows.

29:15.354 --> 29:16.854
Can we--

29:21.793 --> 29:26.396
And now... so do we.

29:27.966 --> 29:29.967
Come here.

