No.

33:01.580 --> 33:05.682
Or any article at all
about your kidnapping?

33:05.684 --> 33:06.583
No.

33:06.585 --> 33:07.517
Look, I know I was kidnapped.

33:07.519 --> 33:09.486
I don't need to read about
the search parties

33:09.488 --> 33:10.387
or how they dredged the lake

33:10.389 --> 33:12.823
and how scary
and awful it all was.

33:12.825 --> 33:13.824
You know how I told you

33:13.826 --> 33:16.460
my birthday was the worst day
of the year?

33:16.462 --> 33:18.628
Actually, it was
the second worst.

33:18.630 --> 33:22.432
The worst day was May 5th.

33:22.434 --> 33:27.070
Carter, you haven't been
celebrating your birthday.

33:27.072 --> 33:30.707
I've been celebrating the day
I was abducted.

33:37.115 --> 33:38.915
(sighs)

33:46.491 --> 33:48.358
(knocking)

33:48.360 --> 33:51.194
Carter, you startled me.

33:51.196 --> 33:54.031
What are you
still doing up?

34:06.511 --> 34:08.879
I saw my mother.

34:15.053 --> 34:17.954
That's all right,
you can tell me.

34:21.159 --> 34:25.629
And she's waiting for me
to run away with her.

34:31.969 --> 34:34.638
She thinks you're coming.

34:36.207 --> 34:39.443
I told her I would.

34:41.813 --> 34:45.482
But-- but now I...

34:46.584 --> 34:47.651
Now you don't want to?

34:47.653 --> 34:50.887
I don't know what I want.

34:52.523 --> 34:53.590
But...

34:53.592 --> 34:59.930
...I can't make this decision.

35:02.333 --> 35:05.001
Where were you
gonna meet her?

35:12.276 --> 35:15.345
She said it was
good for one call

35:15.347 --> 35:18.048
just in case I hit a snag.

35:19.817 --> 35:22.519
(sighs)

35:22.521 --> 35:24.254
I hit a snag.

35:29.060 --> 35:31.761
But I can't call her
and tell her I'm not coming.

35:31.763 --> 35:33.096
You don't have to.
Yes, I do.

35:33.098 --> 35:35.265
Yes, I do have to call her.

35:35.267 --> 35:37.033
I have to call her.

35:37.869 --> 35:43.073
But she'll be hurt
and upset.

35:44.208 --> 35:45.709
And it might be
the last time

35:45.711 --> 35:47.978
I ever hear her voice,

35:47.980 --> 35:52.782
and I'm scared that
I'm gonna say, "I love you,"

35:52.784 --> 35:58.088
and she's not gonna say,
"I love you more," and...

35:58.090 --> 36:01.391
And I can't,
I just can't.

36:01.393 --> 36:02.058
I can't.

36:02.060 --> 36:06.763
It's okay,
it's okay, it's okay.

36:06.765 --> 36:08.632
It's gonna be okay,
I promise.

36:08.634 --> 36:09.432
How?

36:09.434 --> 36:10.734
I will take care of it.

36:10.736 --> 36:15.772
I'm your dad,
and I will take care of it.

36:15.774 --> 36:16.473
How?

36:16.475 --> 36:19.309
Well, I can't tell you.

36:19.311 --> 36:22.312
It's the dad code.

36:30.488 --> 36:36.726
Now, listen, you are too tiny
to carry this enormous burden.

36:36.728 --> 36:39.729
Give it to me and trust me
to take care of it.

36:39.731 --> 36:41.298
Can you do that?

36:44.302 --> 36:45.502
Okay.

36:45.504 --> 36:47.504
Hey.

36:54.145 --> 36:55.745
(sighs)

37:04.755 --> 37:06.456
Hey.

37:11.329 --> 37:13.430
Did you have fun
at the party?

37:13.432 --> 37:14.898
No.

37:17.602 --> 37:22.372
Grant, did you
hear something?

37:22.374 --> 37:25.275
Something that upset you?

37:25.277 --> 37:26.743
Yeah.

37:26.745 --> 37:30.347
Well, it's not true, okay?

37:30.349 --> 37:32.015
No, it's not,
I'm not leaving.

37:32.017 --> 37:32.916
I'm not going anywhere.

37:32.918 --> 37:34.918
Whoa, whoa.
You were gonna leave?

37:34.920 --> 37:36.453
Yeah, isn't that
what you heard?

37:36.455 --> 37:37.721
No, I just heard that now.

37:37.723 --> 37:39.422
But you were gonna leave?

37:39.424 --> 37:41.891
No, I'm not,
I'm not leaving.

37:41.893 --> 37:44.561
That's good.

37:44.563 --> 37:46.463
I'm gonna need you.

37:46.465 --> 37:48.698
We're all gonna need you.

37:49.767 --> 37:51.501
Why?

37:55.373 --> 37:56.106
Forget it.

37:56.108 --> 37:59.075
It's probably just
the sugar talking.

38:01.045 --> 38:02.646
Okay.

38:02.648 --> 38:03.880
Night, Armadillo.

38:03.882 --> 38:06.916
Night, Elephant.

38:06.918 --> 38:08.652
And go to bed.

38:08.654 --> 38:11.388
(sighs)

38:13.824 --> 38:16.626
Quite a day.
Yeah, long.

38:16.628 --> 38:18.094
Like the day
they were born.

38:18.096 --> 38:20.430
Yes, that was a long day.

38:20.432 --> 38:22.265
Oh, my God, twin girls.

38:22.267 --> 38:25.702
Who knew life
could be so good?

38:25.704 --> 38:27.237
Little did we know.

38:27.239 --> 38:29.306
I feel like
it could be good again.

38:29.308 --> 38:31.841
Interesting you should
say that.

38:31.843 --> 38:35.111
Uh, why do you say it's
interesting I should say that?

38:35.113 --> 38:39.349
I wanna talk to you about
a conversation I had today.

38:39.351 --> 38:41.318
Uh-huh.

38:41.320 --> 38:44.754
Lori Stevens has returned.

38:44.756 --> 38:46.022
What?

38:46.024 --> 38:49.726
She was planning to take
our daughter away again today.

38:49.728 --> 38:52.095
It's all right,
no, don't worry.

38:52.097 --> 38:52.896
Carter is here.

38:52.898 --> 38:55.265
She had the chance
to go with Lori.

38:55.267 --> 38:56.800
She chose us.

38:57.635 --> 39:01.004
She chose us.

39:02.006 --> 39:02.539
What's this?

39:02.541 --> 39:04.441
It's where she is
right now.

39:04.443 --> 39:06.109
Lori?

39:06.111 --> 39:07.811
Yeah, waiting for Carter.

39:07.813 --> 39:09.846
I was thinking
what a surprise it would be

39:09.848 --> 39:13.783
if you showed up instead.

39:13.785 --> 39:16.486
(whispering)
As much as I wanna
get this woman, David,

39:16.488 --> 39:20.123
I cannot be the person
to arrest Lori.

39:20.125 --> 39:21.324
I promised Carter.

39:21.326 --> 39:23.626
Well, call the precinct.

39:23.628 --> 39:24.227
Notify the FBI.

39:24.229 --> 39:25.795
This might be
the only chance we get.

39:25.797 --> 39:28.732
She chose to stay with us.

39:28.734 --> 39:31.601
Do you know
how big that is?

39:31.603 --> 39:32.902
I'm okay with that.

39:32.904 --> 39:35.739
Are you sure?

39:35.741 --> 39:38.274
Absolutely sure.

39:40.211 --> 39:42.679
In that case...

39:44.014 --> 39:45.081
...shall we call her

39:45.083 --> 39:48.618
and tell her
Carter's not coming?

39:49.620 --> 39:51.988
Can I see this?

39:54.959 --> 39:55.859
So, if I press
this button, I'll--

39:55.861 --> 40:00.697
You'll be talking to the woman
who stole our daughter.

40:09.407 --> 40:11.374
(phone dials)

40:11.609 --> 40:13.276
<i>Carter, Carter,</i>
<i>is that you?</i>

40:13.278 --> 40:14.644
It's Lori, I can't.

40:14.646 --> 40:15.311
<i>Carter?</i>

40:15.313 --> 40:17.247
It's not Carter,
it's her father.

40:17.249 --> 40:19.015
David.

40:19.017 --> 40:20.884
You wanna talk to Carter?

40:20.886 --> 40:23.553
That's obviously
not gonna happen.

40:23.555 --> 40:25.422
She doesn't want
to talk to you.

40:25.424 --> 40:26.790
That's why I have the phone.

40:26.792 --> 40:29.459
She asked me
to say goodbye for her.

40:29.461 --> 40:31.027
Don't underestimate me, David.

40:31.029 --> 40:33.496
<i>You made that mistake</i>
<i>once before.</i>

40:33.498 --> 40:37.133
By the way,
I've notified the police.

40:37.135 --> 40:39.602
They'll be there any minute.

40:39.604 --> 40:42.238
Yeah, well, you never were
a very good liar.

40:42.240 --> 40:43.840
Goodbye, Lori or Janet,

40:43.842 --> 40:48.144
or whatever you're calling
yourself these days.

40:53.517 --> 40:55.285
You were amazing.

40:55.287 --> 40:58.021
Was I?
Yes, yes.

41:15.840 --> 41:18.675
Mom is having sex
with Gabe's dad.

41:18.677 --> 41:20.076
What is it?
What's wrong?

41:20.078 --> 41:20.910
We need to talk.

41:20.912 --> 41:23.580
No, no.
Oh, my God.

41:23.582 --> 41:25.248
It never ends.

41:25.250 --> 41:26.082
The lies.

41:26.084 --> 41:28.718
I hate you,
now get out of my room.

41:29.220 --> 41:30.453
We are falling apart here.

41:30.455 --> 41:34.123
I've decided
I'm getting divorced.
